movie.title: Exit Humanity
movie.description_intro: A young man's struggle to survive in the aftermath of a deadly undead outbreak during the American Civil War.

movies.title: Lucky Day
movies.summary: Red, a safe cracker who has just been released from prison, is trying to hold his family together as his past catches up with him in the form of Luc, a psychopathic contract killer who's seeking revenge for the death of his brother.

movies.title: The 39 Steps
movies.summary: Richard Hannay is a Canadian visitor to London. At the end of "Mr Memory"'s show in a music hall, he meets Annabella Smith, who is running away from secret agents. He agrees to hide her in his flat, but she is murdered during the night. Fearing that he could be accused of the murder, Hannay goes on the run to break the spy ring.

movies.title: No Man's Land
movies.summary: While travelling through a remote region of Texas in 1866, Rusty Childress and his family are ambushed. When he awakens, he finds his son murdered and his wife missing. Desperate for help, Rusty begrudgingly teams up with a Native American girl who has agreed to help him get his wife back in this action-packed, traditional Western tale.

movies.title: The Silent Natural
movies.summary: William Hoy was one of the first Deaf Major League Baseball players in the 1800's. Being deaf, he introduced hand signals for strike and ball to the game and overcame many obstacles to become one of the greatest players of his time.
